Check whether we go back (`"../"`), stay (`"./"`) or deeper (otherwise), and update the number of `steps`.
```cpp
int minOperations(vector<string>& logs, int steps = 0) {
    for (auto log : logs)
        if (log == "../")
            steps = max(0, steps - 1);
        else if (log != "./")
            ++steps;
    return steps;
}
```

